					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It might sound empiric, but I assume a PPU clock before a memory access. For NTSC, 3 PPU clocks before a memory access, subject to change if a DMC DMA occurs.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><strong>Zepper</strong><br /><a href="http://rocknes.web.fc2.com/" class="postlink"><em>RockNES developer</em></a></div>
